        content: '<div class="doc-section"><div class="doc-section-title">1. Architecture Overview</div><p>The NeuroConversion Engine (NCE) is a proprietary generative AI model deployed dynamically on all product pages.</p></div><div class="doc-section"><div class="doc-section-title">2. Operational Modalities</div><p>The NCE operates across two primary vectors:</p><p>\u2022 Visual: Injecting 5-millisecond colour inversions and micro-geometric pattern shifts into product images. These frames render faster than human ocular processing limits.<br>\u2022 Auditory: Embedding dynamically generated 19kHz acoustic frequencies into auto-playing product videos, matching the neurological resonant frequency for urgency.</p></div><div class="doc-highlight"><strong>System Objective:</strong> Bypass conscious cognitive filters to stimulate the amygdala directly. By deploying cues beneath the threshold of conscious perception, the NCE aims to materially alter the user\'s purchasing behaviour, increasing Average Order Value (AOV) by overriding rational budget constraints.</div>'
