        title: 'Internal Email: Margin Expansion on Simplified Tier',
        date: 'February 20, 2027',
        content: '<div class="doc-section"><p><strong>From:</strong> VP of Commercial Strategy, VitaMatch<br><strong>To:</strong> FlowOptimizer Product Team<br><strong>Subject:</strong> Margin Expansion on Simplified Tier</p><hr><p>Excellent work on the latest FlowOptimizer update. By aggressively routing High-Friction users into the Simplified Tier, we\'ve seen a 45% increase in enrollment for those specific SKUs. Since the Simplified plans have our lowest medical loss ratios (due to the reduced prescription and specialist coverage) and higher monthly premiums, our margins are expanding beautifully.</p><p>These users clearly don\'t have the capacity to compare complex actuarial tables, so giving them a "one-click" expensive option is a win-win. They get a plan without the headache, and we maximize lifetime value. Keep tuning the CLI threshold to capture more of this cohort.</p></div>'
