              judge_response: 'I agree the statistics are concerning, but you must explain why \"guessing based on characteristics\" is a violation of the specific Article 5(1)(d) legal test.',
              legal_reasoning: 'Correct in spirit but lacks statutory precision. It focuses on the "failure" of the system rather than the legal definition of the prohibited practice.'
