              judge_response: 'Counsel, that is a double error. The AI Act applies to all AI systems, not just fully automated ones, and it absolutely protects individuals from law enforcement abuses. It is not a \"consumer protection\" law.',
              legal_reasoning: 'Fundamental error. It invents a "fully automated" requirement and a "consumer only" scope, both of which are completely false under the AI Act.'
