              judge_response: 'Counsel, the AI Act is a fundamental rights regulation that explicitly includes biometric categorisation. Commercial interest does not grant an exemption from Article 5. And biometric data is clearly personal data under EU law.',
              legal_reasoning: 'Fundamental error. It applies the wrong framework (Data Act) and argues that the AI Act doesn\'t apply to marketing, which is legally false.'
