              judge_response: 'I agree that the distinction is a semantic one, but I need you to point to the specific language in Article 5(1)(g) that covers these probabilistic assessments.',
              legal_reasoning: 'Correct in principle but lacks the precise legal application of the term \"infer\" within the Art 5(1)(g) framework.'
