              judge_response: 'Counsel, the AI Act and the MDR are cumulative. And there is no \'data portability\' exemption from risk management obligations. Your argument ignores the fundamental structure of the new Regulation.',
              legal_reasoning: 'Fundamental error. It argues that the AI Act doesn\'t apply (it does, cumulatively with MDR) and invents a non-existent risk management exemption.'
