              judge_response: 'Counsel, that is a double error. The AI Act applies to both \"providers\" and \"deployers,\" and it certainly applies to universities using high-risk systems. There is no \"non-profit\" exemption. Your argument is baseless.',
              legal_reasoning: 'Fundamental error. It invents a \"non-profit\" exemption and wrongly claims the Act doesn\'t apply to deployers like universities.'
