            judge_response: 'I agree that the "human loop" looks compromised, but please address the specific accuracy test in Article 15. How does the definition of "re-offense" affect the legality of the system?',
            legal_reasoning: 'Correct in spirit and uses Evidence 6 well, but lacks statutory precision. It fails to apply the specific Art. 15 legal test for accuracy in relation to the system\'s intended purpose.'
