            legal_reasoning: 'This is the trap. Sentencing AI is a listed High-Risk system (Annex III, 6a). While it feels like \"scoring,\" it does not meet the Article 5(1)(c) definition, which is restricted to social scoring for unrelated contexts. This tests if the student understands the specific scope of prohibitions.'
