      type: 'data',
      title: 'MindMend Homepage Archive',
      date: 'April 2025',
      content: '<div class="doc-section"><div class="doc-section-title">Web Archive: MindMend Landing Page (Q2 2025)</div><div class="doc-highlight" style="font-size: 1.2em; text-align: center; padding: 20px; background-color: #f0f8ff;">"Real Humans. Real Support. Right Now."</div><p><em>Hero Text:</em> Don\'t suffer in silence. Our network of thousands of licensed, compassionate therapists is ready to help you navigate your darkest moments. No wait times, no automated phone trees—just real human connection when you need it most.</p></div><div class="doc-section"><div class="doc-section-title">Footer & Fine Print Analysis</div><p>A review of the website\'s footer and the primary user flow reveals zero mentions of artificial intelligence, chatbots, or automated counseling. The Terms of Service (page 14 of 22) loosely mention the use of "automated tools and secure algorithms," but exclusively in the context of data security and server load-balancing, never indicating that the primary care provider is synthetic.</p></div>'
