            text: 'Your Honour, the respondent\'s attempt to claim a law enforcement exception is legally absurd. The exception in Article 50(1) is strictly limited to AI systems authorized by law to detect, prevent, investigate, or prosecute criminal offenses. MindMend is a private healthcare provider, not a law enforcement agency. Providing crisis support is a medical service, not a criminal investigation. Furthermore, the transcript (Evidence 1) shows a user seeking help for trauma, not a criminal context. Using a narrow public security exception to justify the deceptive commercial deployment of a mental health bot is a gross misapplication of the law.',
