            judge_response: 'The court shares your concern, but I need you to point to the specific statutory provision. Under which Article and which specific Annex do you claim the documentation was insufficient?',
            legal_reasoning: 'Correct in spirit but lacks statutory precision. It focuses on \"honesty\" rather than applying the specific Art 53(1) / Annex XII legal tests.'
