            judge_response: 'Counsel, Aether-Lumina is a commercial model placed on the market. The research exemption only applies *prior* to placing on the market or for purely non-professional research. Your jurisdictional argument is legally baseless.',
            legal_reasoning: 'Fundamental error. It misinterprets the research exemption (Art 2(6)) which does not apply to commercial models placed on the market, and wrongly restricts the Act\'s scope.'
